{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_vllm_disaggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries in disaggregated mode.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode vLLM workers\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "138a1aca-209d-4800-8036-1b46281901e6-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "80d87539-a4a5-4c47-8577-8935ca27a562-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "e024a5be-c2f9-4c3f-be10-33e5ee913fde-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'vllm'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775682901925, "stop": 1775682991722, "uuid": "07f2604a-f853-4764-8a1a-144ccf293ee9", "historyId": "d9fde5f490c6255dd145585d69c1f813", "testCaseId": "414ed8502fd02d47ec818efe41b80e08", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_vllm#test_etcd_ha_failover_vllm_disaggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "vllm"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_1"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "vllm"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha"}, {"name": "suite", "value": "test_vllm"}, {"name": "host", "value": "prod-tester-amd-gpu-v1-phg7c-runner-bs